No. 10-443. Velda Dobson-Davis, Warden, et al., Petitioners v. Kristi Lyn Lunbery. 562 U.S. 1102, 131 S. Ct. 798,

178 L. Ed. 2d 545,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9534. December 6, 2010.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 605 F.3d 754.
